# Placement SLM (Small Language Model)

## Project Overview

Placement SLM is a Small Language Model project developed to demonstrate:

* Small Language Models (SLMs)
* LoRA Fine-Tuning
* Model Training
* Inference
* Evaluation
* Chatbot Deployment using Streamlit

The model is trained on placement preparation question-answer pairs and acts as a Placement Preparation Assistant.

---

# Project Architecture

```text
Dataset
   ↓
Preprocessing
   ↓
DistilGPT2
   ↓
LoRA Fine-Tuning
   ↓
Training
   ↓
Adapter Saving
   ↓
Inference
   ↓
Streamlit Chatbot
```

---

